Interface JavaProcessExecutorService

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Executor, ExecutorService, ProcessExecutor, ProcessExecutorService
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JavaProcessPoolExecutor

    public interface JavaProcessExecutorService
extends ProcessExecutorService, ExecutorService
    An interface for Java process pools that extends both the ProcessExecutorService and ExecutorService interfaces.
    Author:
    Viktor Csomor
